---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About ToolGrid | ToolGrid" description="Learn about our mission to democratize premium web utilities and protect user privacy.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl py-20">
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">About ToolGrid</h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-8">ToolGrid was born out of frustration. As developers and creators, we were tired of searching for simple utilities online—like a background remover or a JSON formatter—only to be met with aggressive paywalls, mandatory account creation, and shady privacy policies.</p>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-8">We noticed a disturbing trend: "Free" tools were never actually free. They were harvesting your data, watermarking your images, and restricting file sizes to upsell you on $15/month subscriptions.</p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-white">The WebAssembly Revolution</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-8">With the advent of WebAssembly (WASM) and modern Browser APIs, we realized we could bypass the cloud entirely. We could compile heavy C++ and Rust libraries—like FFmpeg and ONNX AI models—to run directly inside your Chrome or Safari browser.</p>

      <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-8">This changes the entire economic model of SaaS. Because your computer is doing the heavy lifting, we don't have to pay for expensive cloud compute servers. This allows us to offer premium, enterprise-grade tools absolutely free forever.</p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-white">Our Promise</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-12 marker:text-accent">
        <li><strong>Zero Tracking:</strong> We will never sell your data.</li>
        <li><strong>Zero Uploads:</strong> Your files never touch our servers.</li>
        <li><strong>Zero Fees:</strong> Our tools will remain completely free.</li>
      </ul>
    
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
